title: Waverley Novels. (Abbotsford edition.)
author: Scott, Walter
snippet: But ye have not many of them left,I think-—Mareschal, Airley, Winton, Wemyss, Balmerino, all passed and gone — ay, ay, the countessesand ladies of quality will scarce take up too muchof your ball-room floor with their quality hoopsuow-a-days."
